### Equipment Excel Import/Export API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### 1. Download Equipment Template
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/template
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# File will be downloaded: equipment_import_template_YYYY-MM-DD.xlsx

### 2. Import Equipment from Excel
# Note: Use form-data with key "file" and select the Excel file
POST {{baseUrl}}/equipment/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Response example:
# {
#   "success": 10,
#   "failed": 2,
#   "errors": [
#     {
#       "row": 5,
#       "errors": ["Serial Number \"SN-001\" already exists"]
#     }
#   ],
#   "imported": [...]
# }

### 3. Export All Equipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# File will be downloaded: equipment_export_YYYY-MM-DD.xlsx

### 4. Export Equipment by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Export Equipment by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?category=ROUTER
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Export Equipment by Store
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?storeCode=WAT-BKK-001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Export Equipment by Brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?brand=Cisco
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Export Equipment by Province
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?province=กรุงเทพมหานคร
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Export Expired Warranty Equipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?warrantyExpired=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Export Active Warranty Equipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?warrantyExpired=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Export with Multiple Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export?status=ACTIVE&category=COMPUTER&brand=Dell&province=กรุงเทพมหานคร
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Complete Equipment Management Flow

# Step 1: Download template
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/template
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Step 2: Fill in the template with equipment data
# - Open the downloaded Excel file
# - Fill in equipment information in "ข้อมูลอุปกรณ์" sheet
# - Save the file

###

# Step 3: Import the filled template
POST {{baseUrl}}/equipment/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# [Upload the filled Excel file]

###

# Step 4: Verify imported equipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# Step 5: Export equipment for review
GET {{baseUrl}}/equipment/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes:
# - Maximum 1,000 equipment per import
# - Excel file must be .xlsx format
# - Serial numbers must be unique
# - Store codes must exist in the system
# - Valid categories: NETWORK, COMPUTER, POS, PRINTER, ROUTER, SWITCH, CCTV, OTHER
# - Valid statuses: ACTIVE, INACTIVE, MAINTENANCE, RETIRED
# - Dates must be in YYYY-MM-DD format
